{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And-- so there were all sorts of things going on in-- in Westerbork at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] That's-- that's about all that I-- I can think of in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Westerbork was-- was surrounded by fields of-- of heather, I recall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I'm sorry if so often I think there's nothing more to say, and then I come up with something else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And the heather was of these very lovely shades of lavender and purple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And there were fields of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And then there were flowers, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I don't know what they're called in-- in-- in English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "But a lot of that, I-- I do remember-- not that we could touch the flowers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "They were on the outside of the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "But there was some beauty in that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "And-- and I guess, as children, we looked for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And we looked to see the more positive things in life, because we-- we didn't have that fear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And we didn't have the knowledge that the adults had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "And therefore, we just [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] took everything very, very light, as children normally do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the last few weeks, obviously, were the absolute worst.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were all suffering from malnutrition, dysentery, typhoid, filth, hunger, fear-- that constant fear of not knowing what's to come next.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the hunger, actually, after a while wasn't so painful anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Stomachs shrink after a while.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you don't feel that hunger as-- as much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I weighed 35 pounds, about 16, 17 kilos at the time when we left Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's, as I said, about 35 pounds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was just 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There are really no pictures.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
